    <li class="comment odd alt depth-2" id="dsq-comment-235551">
        <div id="dsq-comment-header-235551" class="dsq-comment-header">
            <cite id="dsq-cite-235551">
                <span id="dsq-author-user-235551">Joel Hruska</span>
            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-235551" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-235551" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Mining isn&#8217;t stealing. When you mine, you aid in the creation of the currency. You are awarded a share of it as value representation of the work.</p>
